Costa Rica üá®üá∑ finca Los Angeles
.
This micromill is one of the only certified organic mills in the area. They are super committed to minimising their environmental impact and have managed to cut their water consumption down to almost nothing by using a special demucilaging machine. Harvesting is done with great care using a brix meter to ensure optimal ripeness. After harvesting the processing is decided based on the weather on the day. This coffee is black honey meaning it only is turned once per day.
.
